Package: ERforResearch
Type: Package
Title: Expected Rank for Research Evaluation
Version: 4.0.0
Authors@R:
    c(person(given = "Rachel",
             family = "Heyard",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "rachel.heyard@snf.ch"))
Description: This package implements the functionality to use the expected ranks (ER) in the context of research evaluation as presented in a recent preprint (https://arxiv.org/abs/2102.09958). For a demonstration of the major functions check out the vignette (Demo ERforResearch).
